eboot hews too closely to its predecessor to transcend the pitfalls of a redundant retread.\"<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/roswell_new_mexico/s01/ |title=Roswell, New Mexico: Season 1 (2019) |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Fandango Media|Fandango]] |accessdate=March 23, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129201548/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/roswell_new_mexico/s01 |archive-date=January 29, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref> [[Metacritic]], which uses a weighted average, assigned the series a score of 58 out of 100 based on 13 critics, indicating \"mixed or average reviews\".<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/tv/roswell-new-mexico |title=Roswell, New Mexico: Season 1 |website=[[Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=January 16, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190116052005/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/roswell-new-mexico |archive-date=January 16, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n===Ratings===\n===Season 1===\n{{Television episode ratings\n| width    = 99\n\n| title1   = [[#ep1|Pilot]]\n| date1    = January 15, 2019\n| rs1      = 0.4/2\n| viewers1 = 1.51<ref name=\"1.01\" />\n| dvr1     = 0.2\n| dvrv1    = 0.92\n| total1   = 0.6\n| totalv1  = 2.43<ref>{{cite web |url=https://programminginsider.com/live7-weekly-ratings-a-million-little-things-just-one-percent-shy-of-season-high-among-adults-18-49-in-its-thursday-debut/ |title=Live+7 Weekly Ratings: 'A Million Little Things' Just One Percent Shy of Season-High Among Adults 18-49 in its Thursday Debut |last=Pucci |first=Douglas |date=February 1, 2019 |work=Programming Insider |accessdate=February 1, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190206030715/https://programminginsider.com/live7-weekly-ratings-a-million-little-things-just-one-percent-shy-of-season-high-among-adults-18-49-in-its-thursday-debut/ |archive-date=February 6, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n| title2   = [[#ep2|So Much for the Afterglow]]\n| date