vision programs]]\n[[Category:Roswell (TV series)]]\n[[Category:Television series by Amblin Entertainment]]\n[[Category:Television series by CBS Television Studios]]\n[[Category:Television series by Warner Bros. Television]]\n[[Category:The CW original programming]]\n[[Category:Television shows set in New Mexico]]\n[[Category:Television programs based on American novels]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2019 science fiction drama television series}}\n{{For|the 1999 TV series|Roswell (TV series)}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2019}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name          = Roswell, New Mexico\n| image              = Roswell-new-mexico-title-card.jpg\n| image_upright      = \n| image_size         = \n| image_alt          = \n| caption            =\n| show_name_2        = \n| genre              = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Drama (film and television)|Drama]]\n* [[Science fiction]]\n* [[Mystery fiction|Mystery]]\n}}\n| based_on           = {{Based on|''[[Roswell High]]''|[[Melinda Metz]]}}\n| developer          = {{Plainlist|\n* Carina Adly MacKenzie\n}}\n| starring           = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Jeanine Mason]]\n* [[Nathan Dean Parsons]]\n* Michael Vlamis\n* Lily Cowles\n* [[Tyler Blackburn]]\n* [[Heather Hemmens]]\n* [[Michael Trevino]]\n* [[Trevor St. John]]\n* Karan Oberoi\n* [[Amber Midthunder]]\n}}\n| narrated           = Jeanine Mason\n| theme_music_composer = \n| opentheme          = \n| endtheme           = \n| composer           = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Michael Suby]]\n* Dennis Smith\n}}\n| country            = United States\n| language           = English\n| num_seasons        = 2<!-- Or num_series. Increment when new seasons/series begin. See template documentation for more info. -->\n| num_episodes       = 18<!-- Value is incremented when new episodes air. See template documentation for more info. -->\n| list_episodes      = #Episodes\n| executive_producer = {{Plainlist|\n* Carina Adly MacKenzie\n* Kevin Kelly Brown\n* Justin Falvey\n* Darryl Frank\n* [[Lawrenc